OL,3,CShocking scale of violence and abuse
OL,4,Cagainst council workers
OL,6,FAlmost 6,000 council workers have
OL,7,Freported assaults and abuse in the
OL,8,Flast three years across Greater
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,FNew figures show teachers, social
OL,12,Fworkers and other front line staff are
OL,13,Fmost likely to be victims of a verbal
OL,14,For physical attack.
OL,16,FData found that abusive incidents are
OL,17,Fbecoming a more regular occurrence,
OL,18,Fwith 2,062 happening in the year
OL,19,Fending March 2025.
