OL,3,CShocking scale of violence and abuse
OL,4,Cagainst council workers
OL,6,FThis is a 17 per cent increase on the
OL,7,F1,832 cases reported by employees and
OL,8,Fcontractors in 2022/23.
OL,10,FHow many assaults on council workers
OL,11,Fwere reported in each local authority
OL,12,Facross Greater Manchester between 2022
OL,13,Fand 2025:
OL,15,FRochdale: 1,931JTameside: 1,169
OL,16,FBolton: 746JManchester: 675JTrafford:
OL,17,F424JWigan: 367JStockport: 356JOldham:
OL,18,F149JSalford: 135JBury: 11
OL,20,FThe worst affected area is Rochdale,
OL,21,Fwith 1,931 assaults.
