OL,6,FA spokesperson for Rochdale Borough
OL,7,FCouncil said: "Council staff work
OL,8,Fextremely hard to deliver services
OL,9,Funder difficult circumstances and
OL,10,Ftheir safety and wellbeing is our
OL,11,Fhighest priority.
OL,13,F"These figures underline the
OL,14,Fchallenges faced by staff who deliver
OL,15,Fservices for residents.
OL,17,F"We take any form of abuse or assault
OL,18,Fagainst staff extremely seriously,
OL,19,Fwith robust policies and measures in
OL,20,Fplace to protect staff and encourage
OL,21,Fthem to report any incidents.
