OL,3,CShocking scale of violence and abuse
OL,4,Cagainst council workers
OL,6,FBut other teams in the council,
OL,7,Fincluding customer services, admin and
OL,8,Fmanagerial staff, also told the
OL,9,Fauthority that they'd suffered a
OL,10,Fphysical or verbal attack.
OL,12,FManchester City Council's report
OL,13,Fshowed that staff were subjected to 15
OL,14,Fracial attacks. Employees impacted by
OL,15,Fthem included a communications
OL,16,Fofficer, five social workers and a
OL,17,Fhomelessness officer. There were also
OL,18,Fsexual assaults against a member of
OL,19,Flibrary staff and five other employees.
